      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 18:31:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长温施称，降息半个百分点的讨论“为时过早”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/ecb-s-wunsch-says-talk-of-half-point-rate-cut-is-premature</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员皮埃尔·温施表示，现在考虑12月份将利率降低半个百分点还为时过早。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/ecb-s-wunsch-says-talk-of-half-point-rate-cut-is-premature</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 18:14:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
